title: Marvel Boy 01-06 + Genesis Edition (2000-2001, Marvel Knights)
description: This is NOT related to my previous Marvel Boy uploads aside from the title - this is the Marvel Knights miniseries written by Grant Morrison that explores Noh-Varr, who would become Captain Marvel for a brief time. All credit to nemesis43 for the original torrent, I have just deleted the extraneous files and reposted it to TPB for easy access. Enjoy and please seed! :-)
